      "Equations with parameters and conditions for a solution to exist",
      "Number of solutions in a given interval",
      "Systems of simultaneous trigonometric equations and common general solutions",
      "Trigonometric inequalities (sin x > k, cos x < k, tan-type)",
      "Range/extrema of trigonometric expressions used to bound solution counts",
      "Equations involving multiple and sub-multiple angles",
      "Sum-to-product and product-to-sum transformations",
      "Boundedness arguments (|sin x| <= 1) to pin down solutions",
      "Periodicity and listing all roots in [0, 2pi)",
      "Locating roots graphically as intersections of curves"
